DESCRIPTION:After suffering a family tragedy\, a widower named Thanh moves
  his two daughters to a centuries-old ancestral home. Both daughters fall
  prey to sleep paralysis and night terrors. Their father seeks the help o
 f a local psychologist\, but chilling secrets and visions eventually prov
 e that all is not what it seems in the old family house.
